original_title: Duke Ellington & Sarah Vaughan  Live At The Berlin Philharmonic Hall 1989
overview: Duke Ellington & His Orchestra plus Sarah Vaughan & Her Trio live in Berlin. Featuring: Duke Ellington (piano), Sarah Vaughan (vocals), Harold Ashby (saxophone), Harry Carney (saxophone), Paul Gonsalves (saxophone), Money Johnson, Gus Mancuso, Russell Procope (saxophone), Eddy Pucci (drums), Norris Turney (saxophone), Johnny Veith (piano), Cootie Williams (trumpet)
title: Duke Ellington & Sarah Vaughan  Live At The Berlin Philharmonic Hall 1989
